Package trust.model.exceptions

Exceptions generated by the framework.

See:
          Description

Exception Summary
DuplicatePeerException Thrown when a peer was added to the framework for tracking twice.
LevelRangeException Thrown when a level is given as a parameter to a method in the framework of an incorrect range.
MalformedTupleException Thrown when a tuple is encountered of an incorrect size.
PeerContextUnfoundException Thrown when information on a peer or context is requested but they have not been previously encountered.
